profile:
Hi :) my name is Leo, I created this channel to show my passion for Supernatural, one of the greatest shows ever created! I`ll be creating videos about the show which include season/episode reactions and reviews, top 10 lists, fun parodies, scene breakdowns, ending explained, news, theories, creatively edited juxtapositions...etc as well as other cool content revolving around the paranormal and Supernatural!. Subscribe to share my Supernatural passion with me!

Juxtapositions and parallels are drawn between different clips to deliver the original narrative of the videos I create in a transformative manner that falls under Fair Use.
